
  Commands Learned
- ls -l  - list all the file and directory 
- chmod  - chnage/modify the file to assign permissions
- chown  - changing ownership
- sudo  - performing actions assuming administrative power

  Permission Structure
r = read  
w = write  
x = execute  

   Numeric Permissions
usually in the format of rwx
7 = rwx  
6 = rw  
5 = rx  
4 = r
